<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Common_features"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Common features</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Emulation"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Emulation</span></a></li>
